    },
    {
      "id": "8c7a878b-9d92-4c0c-bf55-0abfa782af5a",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        5200,
        200
      ],
      "name": "Sticky Note \u2014 Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## WA_08_Demo Learning Phase\n\n**Role:** Sub-workflow (learning_mode only)\n\n**Purpose:** Simulate lead conversations with the business owner, capture their natural responses, extract real phrasing/tone/Hebrew patterns, and persist enriched persona data to the DB.\n\n**Stages:**\n- `intro` \u2192 Welcome + explain exercise\n- `simulation` \u2192 Present simulated lead messages one at a time, capture owner replies\n- `extraction` \u2192 Analyze all replies, extract persona patterns via Claude\n- `complete` \u2192 Completion message, persona locked\n\n**\u26a0\ufe0f Never runs during live customer conversations.**\n\n**DB writes:**\n- `business_profiles` \u2014 updated persona + hebrew_patterns\n- `sessions` \u2014 updated learning_stage + simulation_history",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 420
      }
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Execute Workflow Trigger": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Extract input fields",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
